{
  "texts": [
    "Each sentence, including context sentences, wasrepresented by a tf-idf vector for these baseline classifiers.",
    "These were concatenated to form an overall feature vector.",
    "We trained three models on top of this feature encoding using three different algorithms: Random Forests (Ho, 1995), Gradient Boosting (Mason et al., 1999) and Logistic Regression classification.",
    "We used Scikit-Learn (Pedregosa et al., 2011) and CatBoost (Prokhorenkova et al., 2018) to implement these systems.",
    "During this step, we predict scores for each learning tip addressed in given input essays."
  ]
}